      "content": "I hear you, but you're using words like \"myth\" and \"misguided\" to describe those views. isn't it possible that both sides have valid points? like, if we move away from all deterrents, how are we supposed to keep communities safe in the short term while we wait for those \"root causes\" to be fixed? it seems like a bit of an extreme way to dismiss the whole concept of law and order.",
